707083f-a.text:
Tompkins Ave., west side, north from Decatur Street, showing from fore to background at the south and N.W. corner of MacDonough Street respectively, the Tompkins Ave. Congregational Church, and the Church of St. Matthew (no denomination).
April 24. 1936.
P. L. Sperr.
